{
  "stem": "7177.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think there was-- in a-- on a distance, or in a-- let's say in a-- 3,600 cannons blasted for hours [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] just to get across the Rhine.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the only thing that I remember that we were liberated was-- it was-- all of a sudden, it was-- oh, we had a machine gun, German machine gun, right in front of the barn that we were in, OK?",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For the last couple of days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the last evening of-- what turned out to be the last evening of the actual war that we had-- I could not stay upstairs on the attic.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was so afraid and so scared, and the house next to us was hit and burned down.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I just slid down a rope and sat actually maybe 10 feet away from the German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because-- I was indoors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The soldiers were outdoors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was so afraid that if something happened, I would burn to a crisp, and I couldn't take that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that was what happened that evening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then the following morning, when everything was quiet, one of our [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] underground people came by and whistled a song, 'In Name From Orange,' and the Queen of Holland is the House of Orange.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the Name of the House of Orange, open the door.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You're liberated.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's what he said.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my brother went outside immediately.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I stayed indoors at least three more days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- see, for more than two years, we had trying to hide from everybody.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You couldn't-- you know, if your face showed any place, that brought the people in danger who were hiding us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I felt just like the nuns who had taught me how to play the piano.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
